snippet.title: Zombies Reveal Trailer | Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III
snippet.description:
If we fail, they get through…and we lose everything 🧟‍♂️ 

Make your way through the open world in a fight for survival against the undead in #ModernWarfareZombies #CODNext
